00:48:52.450 --> 00:48:55.384
Gravity slows things down.
And so, in principle,

00:48:55.384 --> 00:48:58.496
if you've got enough mass,
the Universe will stop,

00:48:58.496 --> 00:49:00.719
turn around,
and fall backwards.

00:49:00.719 --> 00:49:04.024
And you can compute from--we
will compute,

00:49:04.024 --> 00:49:07.490
next period,
how fast you have to go to make

00:49:07.490 --> 00:49:09.377
that happen.
